query:
SELECT 
  CASE 
    WHEN questionText LIKE '%EU AI Act%' THEN 'EU AI Act'
    WHEN questionText LIKE '%NIST%' THEN 'NIST RMF'
    WHEN questionText LIKE '%TC260%' THEN 'TC260'
    WHEN questionText LIKE '%ethics%' OR questionText LIKE '%Ethics%' OR questionText LIKE '%bias%' THEN 'Ethics'
    ELSE 'Incident Analysis'
  END as category,
  COUNT(*) as count
FROM test_questions
GROUP BY category
ORDER BY count DESC;
